725595f-a.title: Queens: 71st Avenue - 79th Lane
725595f-a.text:
Seventy-first Avenue (formerly Haverkamp Place) north side
between 79th Lane and Dry Harbor Road, showing in two views the
white building, belonging to Theodore Day in 1873 and one Haverkamp
in 1896.
May 1923
View 2March 1925
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
